divs: sighting detailsmy roommate and i were standing outside of our apartment and noticed two objects flying towards our location from over the tree line. the objects were glowing the color of a burning cigarette butt with a slightly off center red light. the two objects slowly flew overhead at about the speed of a helicopter. after moving overhead they began to ascend in an arc shape up into the sky until out of sight. the overall experience lasted about 2 1\2-4 minutes in a highly populated area.
Summary: Two distinct objects giving off bright yellowish orange glow with a slightly off center red light
